name: Predator Cybercats - Argonaut
description: Legendary beast that commands a peace keeping legion across the cosmos. His leadership, honor, and raw power are unmatched. There has not been a foe in his galaxy he has not been able to defeat. Titanium exterior, core powered by rare unknown crystal capable of discharging an energetic blast that can knockout or kill depending on the distance from the blast. Diamond teeth able to shred through most materials known to man. The strong silent type.
